1
00:01:31,100 --> 00:01:34,980
=Wonder Wall=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,910
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,159
I need to pee.

4
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,359
Watch them.

5
00:01:58,359 --> 00:02:00,519
I need to go too.

6
00:02:02,159 --> 00:02:03,280
I can't hold it.

7
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,799
Hurry up.

8
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,560
Don't get smart with me.

9
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:08,120
Or you will regret it.

10
00:02:08,319 --> 00:02:09,280
I'm old.

11
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,520
Not like you.

12
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,800
You are young and quick.

13
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:13,840
I'm old. I can't get far.

14
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,439
Hurry up.

15
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,960
I will take her too.

16
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,159
Wenwen, run!

17
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,120
Run!

18
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:40,639
What are you doing?

19
00:02:40,639 --> 00:02:41,319
Run, Wenwen!

20
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:41,719
What are you doing?

21
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:42,280
Zhan Chun!

22
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,039
Stop!

23
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,960
She's running! Get her!

24
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,120
Don't look back! Run, Wenwen!

25
00:03:00,439 --> 00:03:01,360
Run!

26
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,840
Come on!

27
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:12,039
You bit me?

28
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,520
You little brat.

29
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,560
Dad!

30
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,240
Yu Ming!

31
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:19,560
Get in!

32
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,080
Don't fight me.

33
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,159
Wenwen, don't be scared.

34
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:28,759
It is okay, Wenwen.

35
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,759
You are okay.

36
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,400
I want to go home.

37
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:40,879
He's back.

38
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,120
- Where did he go?
- Calm down.

39
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:43,240
Relax.

40
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,000
So you do know the way back.

41
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:44,520
Mom.

42
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,280
You remember I'm your mother?

43
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,759
Mom.

44
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,400
Where were you?

45
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,400
Every time Wenwen is with you,

46
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,719
something goes wrong.

47
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,560
If anything

48
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,479
happens to Wenwen,

49
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:54,319
I will never let you off.

50
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,159
Get Wenwen back. Now!

51
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,360
All right. All right.

52
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,879
Don't get worked up.

53
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,280
Hello?

54
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,599
Fan Meijuan.

55
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:03,520
Yu Wenwen.

56
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,919
15 million each.

57
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,080
30 million for both.

58
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:07,680
Get the money ready. Wait for my call.

59
00:04:07,800 --> 00:04:08,439
Who are you?

60
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:09,199
Where are you?

61
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:09,919
Talk to me!

62
00:04:10,759 --> 00:04:12,199
Where is my granddaughter?

63
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,319
Give her back right now!

64
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,719
Or I'm calling the police!

65
00:04:14,919 --> 00:04:15,479
Police?

66
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,360
Try it.

67
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:17,040
Call the police,

68
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,560
and I'll cut their throats.

69
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,399
You...

70
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:22,720
He hung up.

71
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:23,879
Call him back.

72
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,639
Look at me.

73
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,000
Old lady.

74
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,000
Come on.

75
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,160
No. Not this one.

76
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:36,959
Look at me. Just look at me!

77
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,480
Don't you understand my words?

78
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,600
Look at me.

79
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,680
You. Look at me.

80
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,439
Why are you all so stubborn?

81
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,800
Come on.

82
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:54,959
Ma'am.

83
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,000
Don't call me that.

84
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,319
That money

85
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:05,360
is not yours either.

86
00:05:06,279 --> 00:05:07,639
Part of it is our wages.

87
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,120
Once we get paid,

88
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,360
we will let you go.

89
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,800
Keep fighting us,

90
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:13,600
and things get ugly.

91
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,240
So work with us.

92
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,720
Okay. This works.

93
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,160
Look here.

94
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,120
How is it?

95
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:40,759
The photos...

96
00:05:42,199 --> 00:05:42,680
Mom.

97
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:43,279
Give it to me.

98
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,879
Mom. Mom.

99
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,439
I said give it to me!

100
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,199
Did you hear me?

101
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:54,680
Call...

102
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:55,240
Call...

103
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:55,720
Call...

104
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,199
Call him...

105
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:56,720
I will. I will.

106
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:57,560
I'm calling.

107
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,600
Call him...

108
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,240
I am.

109
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,360
I am. Mom.

110
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:01,560
I'm calling.

111
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:03,879
Lanying!

112
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:04,199
Mom!

113
00:06:04,639 --> 00:06:04,920
Lanying!

114
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,360
Mom!

115
00:06:05,727 --> 00:06:09,500
(Outpatient)

116
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,639
How could you let her

117
00:06:10,879 --> 00:06:12,319
see these photos?

118
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,800
She just grabbed it from me.

119
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,240
She's always like this.

120
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,360
Hotheaded and impulsive.

121
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,800
What about Yitong?

122
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:20,560
What will you tell her?

123
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,319
I have not figured it out.

124
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,439
She panics easily too.

125
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:32,839
Family of Sun Lanying?

126
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,240
Yes.

127
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,759
I got you an extra slot.

128
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:36,560
Go upstairs to Neurology.

129
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,000
You go. I'll stay with her.

130
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,000
Pay the bill first.

131
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,079
These are the results

132
00:06:55,079 --> 00:06:55,560
from the CT scan.

133
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:58,319
Her cerebral arteries hardened.

134
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,079
The vessels are narrowed.

135
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,759
When she gets emotional,

136
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,240
her blood pressure keeps fluctuating.

137
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,120
That reduces blood flow to the brain.

138
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,720
These two conditions

139
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:08,720
affect each other.

140
00:07:08,879 --> 00:07:09,360
As her family,

141
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,600
you need to be very careful.

142
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:12,800
If it gets serious,

143
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:14,079
what could happen?

144
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:15,480
It could cause cardiac arrest.

145
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:17,079
You must keep her

146
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:18,639
from getting emotionally worked up.

147
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:19,680
Avoid upsetting her.

148
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,600
She has been very agitated.

149
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:22,759
Why is she

150
00:07:22,959 --> 00:07:24,160
so agitated?

151
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,560
She does not seem to have

152
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,800
any psychiatric issues.

153
00:07:28,399 --> 00:07:29,839
Something happened.

154
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,240
Her grandchild is missing.

155
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,360
What?

156
00:07:40,650 --> 00:07:42,521
(Wen Yitong)

157
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,040
Hello, Yitong.

158
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,480
I can't reach Yu Ming.

159
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,480
Is he with you?

160
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,160
Let's take the stairs.

161
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,720
Sorry. Sorry.

162
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:28,639
I'm sorry.

163
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,519
What is wrong with you?

164
00:08:29,519 --> 00:08:30,839
Why are you so careless?

165
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:34,120
Ming.

166
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,120
Are you okay?

167
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,639
I'm fine.

168
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,200
Don't rush too much.

169
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,039
Mom is this sick.

170
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:43,919
Wenwen and her grandma are missing.

171
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:46,240
Whatever monsters they are,

172
00:08:46,919 --> 00:08:48,360
however cruel they may be,

173
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,559
I will bring them back.

174
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:56,799
I'm sorry. Sorry.

175
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,879
Yitong called me.

176
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:58,960
She kept asking.

177
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,279
I couldn't keep it from her.

178
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:01,440
I'm sorry.

179
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,200
It's Yitong.

180
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:07,279
Answer it.

181
00:09:08,399 --> 00:09:09,320
The longer you hide it,

182
00:09:09,399 --> 00:09:10,320
the worse it gets.

183
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:16,519
Hi.

184
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,679
So you were not going to tell me?

185
00:09:19,879 --> 00:09:20,879
When were you planning to let me know?

186
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,039
After they killed them?

187
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,399
Were they kidnapped?

188
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:24,000
Were they?

189
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:24,799
Yes.

190
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:27,360
I didn't know how to tell you.

191
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:28,960
And now, Mom has collapsed.

192
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:30,799
How much do they want?

193
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:31,759
30 million.

194
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:32,720
Give them.

195
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,240
Whatever they ask, do it.

196
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:38,879
Yitong said she is going to Unit 505.

197
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,360
Take care of my mom.

198
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,279
Take a break. Let me do it.

199
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:15,279
I got it. I got it.

200
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,679
Easy. Easy.

201
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,080
Before, they sat on the money

202
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:23,639
and refused to admit a thing.

203
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,600
Now, they can't wait to give it back.

204
00:10:27,440 --> 00:10:28,639
Blood has been spilled.

205
00:10:30,159 --> 00:10:31,080
They are scared.

206
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,440
Money.

207
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,240
It always makes fools of people.

208
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,960
Text him.

209
00:10:43,052 --> 00:10:45,496
(Hopefully, next time we meet,
we both get what we want.)

210
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,919
What does he mean, "meet"?

211
00:10:48,559 --> 00:10:49,080
Think about it.

212
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:50,759
Who knows about the 30 million?

213
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:51,480
Besides Hong Jinkui

214
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,159
and us.

215
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:52,679
Who else?

216
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,159
Li Jin.

217
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:53,759
Zinuo's mother.

218
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,639
It has to be her.

219
00:10:54,639 --> 00:10:55,960
She knows about the 30 million,

220
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,399
and she is capable of kidnapping.

221
00:10:57,519 --> 00:10:57,919
Right?

222
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,919
Hong Jinkui is dead.

223
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,120
If not her, then who?

224
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,320
Let me call her.

225
00:11:08,559 --> 00:11:08,960
Hello?

226
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,720
Where did you take them?

227
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,399
Didn't we tell you

228
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:13,679
we would return everything?

229
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,720
Didn't we tell you

230
00:11:14,720 --> 00:11:15,919
we would cooperate?

231
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:16,879
What is this stunt

232
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,639
supposed to mean?

233
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:18,559
You spent five years inside.

234
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:19,440
Was that not enough?

235
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,519
Have you lost your mind?

236
00:11:20,559 --> 00:11:21,360
I'm telling you,

237
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,759
if anything happens to them,

238
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:24,039
you will rot in prison!

239
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:24,759
And Chen Zinuo

240
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:26,320
will never hold her head up again!

241
00:11:26,399 --> 00:11:27,480
You are being reckless.

242
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,639
Don't provoke her!

243
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:32,240
What good does yelling do?

244
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,279
I wanted to scare her.

245
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,960
Does she think I'm a pushover?

246
00:11:35,039 --> 00:11:36,120
What does this call

247
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,919
solve right now?

248
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,639
Tell me.

249
00:11:42,519 --> 00:11:43,480
I told you,

250
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,399
don't provoke her!

251
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,559
His family has been kidnapped.

252
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,440
Looks like

253
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:53,519
someone else is after the money.

254
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:55,000
Weird.

255
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:56,480
Everyone who knew about it,

256
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,080
I already dealt with them.

257
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,240
Clearly, not clean enough.

258
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,240
Answer it.

259
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,320
Hello?

260
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:09,960
The ones being kidnapped...

261
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:10,879
Sir, 60 million for two people.

262
00:12:10,879 --> 00:12:11,360
We will give you.

263
00:12:11,399 --> 00:12:12,039
All of them.

264
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,279
We will give you everything we have.

265
00:12:13,279 --> 00:12:13,759
Okay?

266
00:12:16,039 --> 00:12:17,639
We don't have 60 million now.

267
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:18,399
The two million

268
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:20,000
went to San and the others.

269
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:20,360
Sir.

270
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,799
We have 58 million now.

271
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:22,840
That is everything

272
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:23,639
we have left.

273
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,120
We...

274
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,440
We will give it all to you.

275
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,919
58 million is still a lot.

276
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:27,679
With that money,

277
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:29,080
you can live very well, okay?

278
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,080
Yes, 58 million is a lot.

279
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,720
Please, it's an elder and a child.

280
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:32,759
Don't hurt them. Please don't.

281
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:33,240
This house...

282
00:12:33,240 --> 00:12:34,120
The house is worth five million.

283
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,799
Sir, five million.

284
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:35,080
Please.

285
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,240
You can have the house too.

286
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:36,679
Okay?

287
00:12:36,679 --> 00:12:37,279
All of it.

288
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,120
Everything. Please.

289
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:38,559
Okay?

290
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:43,879
Fine.

291
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,799
Get the 58 million ready.

292
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:46,440
Wait for my call.

293
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:53,039
58 million.

294
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,480
Who would say no to more money?

295
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:02,440
We need to move fast.

296
00:13:02,759 --> 00:13:03,320
She is crazy.

297
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,080
I will go to talk to Zinuo.

298
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:04,799
Okay.

299
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,360
For now, the treatment

300
00:13:12,399 --> 00:13:13,600
will focus on thrombolysis

301
00:13:13,879 --> 00:13:15,200
to improve cerebral blood flow.

302
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,279
But you should be prepared.

303
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,159
She may develop

304
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,000
paralysis or slurred speech.

305
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,919
As for her prognosis,

306
00:13:23,399 --> 00:13:24,399
it's too early to say.

307
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,759
Have you found the child?

308
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:28,960
Not yet.

309
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,600
You need to find the kid quickly.

310
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,240
After she wakes up,

311
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,600
the worst thing for her

312
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,480
is another major emotional shock.

313
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:36,840
That could make

314
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:37,919
her condition much worse.

315
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,159
Thank you.

316
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:05,960
Sir.

317
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:06,840
Yes?

318
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:10,320
I need ten of these cases.

319
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:10,840
Do you have them?

320
00:14:11,279 --> 00:14:12,240
How many? Ten?

321
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:12,799
Ten.

322
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:13,799
Yes, no problem.

323
00:14:13,879 --> 00:14:14,720
I will pack them now.

324
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:15,679
Have a seat.

325
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:21,360
Eat something first.

326
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:24,440
♪Hoarded wealth♪

327
00:14:24,799 --> 00:14:27,039
You haven't eaten
since yesterday afternoon.

328
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:28,559
They are still missing,

329
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,799
so we can't break down.

330
00:14:29,799 --> 00:14:32,000
♪Behind smiling faces♪

331
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:35,080
♪Holding on to grudges♪

332
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,120
Why Sichuan food?

333
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,760
♪Becomes your prison♪

334
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:39,039
♪Desire feeds illusions♪

335
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:39,919
You like it.

336
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:43,320
♪Leaving nothing behind♪

337
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,600
Not as good as my mom's cooking.

338
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,640
♪Greed and cunning♪

339
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:48,159
I shouldn't have let her come.

340
00:14:48,159 --> 00:14:49,560
♪Only bring ruin upon oneself♪

341
00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:51,200
♪Without trust♪

342
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:54,280
♪One sails alone through life♪

343
00:14:55,321 --> 00:14:57,560
♪A kind heart lights the path♪

344
00:14:57,649 --> 00:15:00,720
♪Through the darkest night♪

345
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,320
♪After hardship♪

346
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:05,320
♪The fog clears and the sun rises♪

347
00:15:06,128 --> 00:15:08,200
♪The dream of fame and fortune ends♪

348
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:11,080
♪True hearts are revealed
in times of trial♪

349
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:17,640
♪A good and honest life
is all that truly matters♪

350
00:15:19,759 --> 00:15:20,279
Dad.

351
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:21,960
Is Mom awake?

352
00:15:23,039 --> 00:15:23,919
Your mom is fine.

353
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:25,360
I'm here with her.

354
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,480
You two need to stay safe.

355
00:15:28,559 --> 00:15:29,919
Did the kidnappers call?

356
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:33,240
So you are taking them the money?

357
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:35,759
Once they get it,

358
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:37,080
they will let them go.

359
00:15:38,559 --> 00:15:39,440
Ming.

360
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:41,840
You are a good man.

361
00:15:43,799 --> 00:15:44,679
But you know,

362
00:15:46,159 --> 00:15:47,360
to us,

363
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:49,159
you matter most.

364
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:50,879
Don't get into

365
00:15:51,799 --> 00:15:53,399
any conflict with the kidnappers.

366
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:57,360
There is no shame in backing down.

367
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:00,360
Your safety comes first.

368
00:16:01,679 --> 00:16:03,519
The whole family depends on you.

369
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:05,879
For your family,

370
00:16:06,639 --> 00:16:07,879
bowing your head

371
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,120
doesn't make you weak.

372
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:14,320
Remember to eat on time.

373
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:18,559
Good boy.

374
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:38,840
Zinuo.

375
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:40,399
Ouyang.

376
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:41,519
Listen to me first.

377
00:16:41,759 --> 00:16:42,679
Your mom kidnapped

378
00:16:42,799 --> 00:16:43,519
Yu Wenwen

379
00:16:43,759 --> 00:16:44,600
and Wen Yitong's mother for money.

380
00:16:44,879 --> 00:16:45,639
Yu Ming has the money ready.

381
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:46,480
He can give it to her anytime.

382
00:16:46,679 --> 00:16:47,639
Tell her not to do anything rash.

383
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,480
Where are you going?

384
00:16:53,559 --> 00:16:54,679
The show is about to start.

385
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,360
Everyone.

386
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:56,559
I called you all here today

387
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,360
because this is serious.

388
00:16:57,919 --> 00:16:58,720
My benefactor,

389
00:16:58,759 --> 00:17:00,039
Mr. Yu, who saved my life,

390
00:17:00,159 --> 00:17:01,480
needs our help urgently.

391
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,120
Yesterday, just yesterday,

392
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:04,599
his daughter and mother-in-law

393
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,200
went missing.

394
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,240
They still haven't been found.

395
00:17:06,279 --> 00:17:07,400
Qian Weijie, what are you doing?

396
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:08,599
Did you forget

397
00:17:08,599 --> 00:17:09,880
how they played us before?

398
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:11,960
That is Zihan's school money.

399
00:17:12,240 --> 00:17:13,480
Whatever happened, she is my niece.

400
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:14,359
How can I ignore this?

401
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,200
Hello, Mr. Hou.

402
00:17:16,279 --> 00:17:17,400
I sent you the photos

403
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,079
of the two missing people.

404
00:17:18,279 --> 00:17:18,839
Please contact

405
00:17:18,839 --> 00:17:19,839
the travel agency drivers

406
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:20,480
and ask them to keep an eye out.

407
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:21,680
If there is any news,

408
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,799
please tell me right away.

409
00:17:24,039 --> 00:17:25,240
Did everyone get the message?

410
00:17:25,519 --> 00:17:26,279
Yes.

411
00:17:26,279 --> 00:17:27,359
Split up and search.

412
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:28,599
Every second counts.

413
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,440
Go!

414
00:17:29,599 --> 00:17:30,119
Go!

415
00:17:30,359 --> 00:17:31,599
Their information and photos

416
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:32,440
have been sent

417
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,160
to the car club group.

418
00:17:33,359 --> 00:17:33,920
Now,

419
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,039
let's not waste time.

420
00:17:35,079 --> 00:17:36,000
Everyone, move!

421
00:17:36,119 --> 00:17:36,559
Okay?

422
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,400
- Okay!
- Go!

423
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:51,960
Open the door!

424
00:17:53,519 --> 00:17:54,039
Li Jin.

425
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,079
Open up!

426
00:17:58,319 --> 00:17:58,920
Li Jin.

427
00:18:18,950 --> 00:18:21,028
(Chen Zinuo)

428
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:23,680
Hello?

429
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,279
I know what you are doing.

430
00:18:25,799 --> 00:18:26,599
She is with you now,

431
00:18:26,599 --> 00:18:27,200
isn't she?

432
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:31,960
Don't say anything.

433
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:32,880
Just listen.

434
00:18:34,079 --> 00:18:34,559
Okay.

435
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,319
Let them go now.

436
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,319
I promise Yu Ming will let it go.

437
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:39,799
But if anything happens to them,

438
00:18:40,039 --> 00:18:40,559
none of us

439
00:18:40,559 --> 00:18:41,359
will get out of this clean.

440
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,400
Stay out of things

441
00:18:44,839 --> 00:18:45,640
that are not yours.

442
00:18:46,359 --> 00:18:47,680
I'm not meddling, Lei.

443
00:18:47,799 --> 00:18:48,799
Do you know

444
00:18:48,799 --> 00:18:49,519
the consequences?

445
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:50,640
Fine.

446
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,839
Say you get the money.

447
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:52,880
Then what?

448
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,240
You know Li Jin.

449
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,240
Chen Liyang is the warning.

450
00:18:59,359 --> 00:18:59,920
Don't worry.

451
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,119
It's all covered.

452
00:19:04,359 --> 00:19:05,400
Where are they now?

453
00:19:09,599 --> 00:19:10,400
Don't ask that.

454
00:19:16,279 --> 00:19:17,920
The van for the money is ready.

455
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,720
Just as you said,

456
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:21,839
an older model.

457
00:19:22,599 --> 00:19:23,680
The plate has been changed too.

458
00:19:24,079 --> 00:19:25,200
An Ancheng plate.

459
00:19:26,279 --> 00:19:26,839
Good.

460
00:19:27,319 --> 00:19:28,079
Please think of something.

461
00:19:28,079 --> 00:19:28,519
Please.

462
00:19:28,519 --> 00:19:29,200
Wenwen is stubborn.

463
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,119
She always has been.

464
00:19:30,119 --> 00:19:31,279
I'm afraid she'll anger them.

465
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:31,880
And

466
00:19:32,039 --> 00:19:33,200
Ms. Fan isn't well.

467
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:34,599
She can't take this kind of stress.

468
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,680
I can't promise that.

469
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:40,799
But I know Li Jin.

470
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:43,480
As long as she gets what she wants,

471
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:45,359
she won't make trouble.

472
00:19:45,519 --> 00:19:46,240
I understand.

473
00:19:46,319 --> 00:19:46,960
The money is ready.

474
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,039
They will have it.

475
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:48,880
So you have to

476
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,000
talk your mom down.

477
00:19:50,319 --> 00:19:51,720
Wenwen is his brother's child.

478
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:52,759
She is his whole life.

479
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,279
Please. I'm begging you.

480
00:20:12,005 --> 00:20:13,703
(Chun'an County, Luzhou City)

481
00:20:16,359 --> 00:20:17,960
There is a van at this location.

482
00:20:18,279 --> 00:20:19,720
Put the money in it.

483
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:52,880
Is this it?

484
00:21:03,079 --> 00:21:04,759
♪Work hard and make money♪

485
00:21:04,839 --> 00:21:05,720
(Unknown Number)
♪I want to get rich♪

486
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:06,260
(Unknown Number)

487
00:21:07,119 --> 00:21:07,640
Hello?

488
00:21:08,160 --> 00:21:09,000
Once the money is loaded,

489
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,759
call this number.

490
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,880
He can see us.

491
00:21:21,559 --> 00:21:22,000
Don't provoke him.

492
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:22,880
I will go get the money.

493
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,039
We need backup too.

494
00:21:26,920 --> 00:21:27,960
Ouyang?

495
00:21:28,599 --> 00:21:29,359
Jiajia?

496
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,960
We are taking the money
to the kidnappers.

497
00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:32,200
Wait for me in Unit 505.

498
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:11,920
How is it?

499
00:22:12,119 --> 00:22:12,880
What's happening now?

500
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:13,839
Has the money gone out?

501
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,000
I don't know. I just got here.

502
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,039
One, two, three.

503
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,480
Okay.

504
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,200
Your phone.

505
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,079
♪A villa by the sea♪

506
00:22:38,079 --> 00:22:39,079
♪Seafood every day♪

507
00:22:40,839 --> 00:22:41,960
The money is loaded.

508
00:22:42,440 --> 00:22:43,599
I will send you another address.

509
00:22:46,440 --> 00:22:47,720
I will follow you in your car.

510
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:48,640
I can help if anything happens.

511
00:22:49,279 --> 00:22:50,039
Here are the keys.

512
00:22:51,893 --> 00:22:53,300
(Sandao Valley)

513
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,440
He sent the location.

514
00:22:54,480 --> 00:22:55,000
Let's go.

515
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:00,759
Great-grandma.

516
00:23:02,279 --> 00:23:03,039
This trip,

517
00:23:03,759 --> 00:23:04,680
just like you said,

518
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,640
we met a kind benefactor.

519
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,000
We got our money back.

520
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,599
We even bought a van.

521
00:23:11,519 --> 00:23:12,720
I won't leave for work anymore.

522
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,160
I will drive a taxi

523
00:23:16,279 --> 00:23:16,960
and spend more time with you.

524
00:23:19,039 --> 00:23:20,359
Mr. Yu is a good man.

525
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:21,640
If not for him,

526
00:23:22,039 --> 00:23:23,119
we would never have got our money.

527
00:23:33,519 --> 00:23:33,960
Great-grandma.

528
00:23:34,279 --> 00:23:34,759
What's wrong?

529
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,480
What is it?

530
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:36,640
Don't scare me.

531
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:37,240
What...

532
00:23:38,279 --> 00:23:40,079
Why, whenever I mention Mr. Yu,

533
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:40,920
do you start knocking?

534
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,319
Did something

535
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:43,160
happen to him?

536
00:23:44,079 --> 00:23:44,599
Great-grandma.

537
00:23:46,039 --> 00:23:46,920
Say something.

538
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:50,119
What...

539
00:23:50,559 --> 00:23:51,680
She fell asleep now?

540
00:24:31,319 --> 00:24:32,799
A good horse sees no ditch.

541
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,000
A coward sees only hurdles.

542
00:24:35,279 --> 00:24:36,599
Once we get Wenwen and your mom back,

543
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:38,160
we start a new life.

544
00:24:38,519 --> 00:24:39,279
That is our victory.

545
00:24:45,079 --> 00:24:45,720
Gauze.

546
00:24:45,720 --> 00:24:47,000
Alcohol, iodine.

547
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:47,599
Cold medicine.

548
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,319
Medicine for bruises and sprains.

549
00:24:49,559 --> 00:24:50,680
Are we missing anything?

550
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,640
I packed some food too.

551
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:52,279
Who knows how long

552
00:24:52,279 --> 00:24:53,039
they have gone without eating.

553
00:25:08,839 --> 00:25:09,880
This is it, right?

554
00:25:15,240 --> 00:25:16,000
(Leave the van.)

555
00:25:16,359 --> 00:25:17,440
(I sent you where they are.)

556
00:25:17,720 --> 00:25:18,519
(Go find them yourselves.)

557
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,240
Go. Go.

558
00:26:19,599 --> 00:26:20,160
- Hey.
- San.

559
00:26:20,839 --> 00:26:21,519
What happened?

560
00:26:22,119 --> 00:26:23,000
Why call me over this late?

561
00:26:23,039 --> 00:26:24,000
I was half asleep.

562
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,279
Great-grandma said

563
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:26,680
something happened to Mr. Yu.

564
00:26:28,079 --> 00:26:29,160
She can talk now?

565
00:26:29,359 --> 00:26:29,799
No.

566
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:30,960
When I was

567
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:31,880
washing her feet,

568
00:26:32,119 --> 00:26:32,960
I mentioned Mr. Yu,

569
00:26:33,119 --> 00:26:34,400
and she started tapping her cane.

570
00:26:34,519 --> 00:26:35,319
She kept tapping.

571
00:26:35,480 --> 00:26:36,279
Scared me to death.

572
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,799
Last time she tapped like that

573
00:26:37,799 --> 00:26:38,640
was four or five years ago.

574
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:40,480
Two people passed by.

575
00:26:40,480 --> 00:26:41,960
She kept tapping and tapping.

576
00:26:42,039 --> 00:26:42,680
A few days later,

577
00:26:42,799 --> 00:26:43,519
there was heavy rain.

578
00:26:43,559 --> 00:26:44,559
A mudslide hit their village,

579
00:26:44,559 --> 00:26:45,559
and those two died.

580
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:47,480
Right.

581
00:26:47,759 --> 00:26:48,279
Exactly.

582
00:26:48,480 --> 00:26:49,160
Then...

583
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,440
Did you ask her

584
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,880
what happened to Mr. Yu?

585
00:26:52,119 --> 00:26:53,160
I was just about to,

586
00:26:53,559 --> 00:26:54,400
then she fell asleep.

587
00:26:54,559 --> 00:26:55,119
Let's go.

588
00:26:55,119 --> 00:26:55,759
Let's ask her.

589
00:26:55,759 --> 00:26:56,759
Ask her.

590
00:26:56,759 --> 00:26:57,880
- Go.
- Wait.

591
00:26:57,880 --> 00:26:58,440
Let's ask her.

592
00:26:58,480 --> 00:26:59,480
Ask your great-grandma.

593
00:26:59,559 --> 00:27:00,519
No, no.

594
00:27:01,759 --> 00:27:02,759
When my great-grandma falls asleep,

595
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,039
