Just not this.

893
00:38:12,159 --> 00:38:13,320
I'm disappointed.

894
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:17,199
Still, I must catch her if she falls.

895
00:38:25,239 --> 00:38:25,679
Hello?

896
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:28,880
Good.

897
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,480
I will have the money sent over.

898
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,320
I sent you the address.

899
00:38:38,119 --> 00:38:38,840
Be careful on the way.

900
00:38:40,039 --> 00:38:40,519
I will.

901
00:39:27,599 --> 00:39:28,440
Wenwen.

902
00:39:30,639 --> 00:39:33,000
I don't think I'm going home.

903
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,679
I may never

904
00:39:37,760 --> 00:39:40,239
cook for you again.

905
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:42,519
When you are on your own,

906
00:39:42,679 --> 00:39:45,840
remember to have less fried chicken.

907
00:39:46,119 --> 00:39:47,280
That's not true, Grandma.

908
00:39:48,559 --> 00:39:49,239
Dad and Mom

909
00:39:49,239 --> 00:39:50,480
will be here soon.

910
00:39:51,599 --> 00:39:52,480
When you get better,

911
00:39:52,639 --> 00:39:54,199
I still want your spicy chicken.

912
00:39:58,079 --> 00:40:00,760
Listen to your Mom and Dad.

913
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,960
I know my daughter.

914
00:40:04,039 --> 00:40:04,880
She truly sees you

915
00:40:04,880 --> 00:40:07,440
as her own child.

916
00:40:08,079 --> 00:40:08,880
I know.

917
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:11,400
My mom is

918
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,360
the toughest mom in the world.

919
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:14,599
But she's never been harsh with me.

920
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,199
Do you remember

921
00:40:17,199 --> 00:40:19,440
when you first met me?

922
00:40:21,039 --> 00:40:22,320
You were afraid of me.

923
00:40:24,039 --> 00:40:25,800
I did that on purpose.

924
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:27,400
I wanted you to fear me.

925
00:40:27,480 --> 00:40:28,199
I know.

926
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:30,480
I acted like I didn't like you.

927
00:40:30,639 --> 00:40:31,440
Because

928
00:40:31,599 --> 00:40:33,519
deep down, I felt

929
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:35,519
my daughter had suffered too much.

930
00:40:35,599 --> 00:40:36,599
You didn't know,

931
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,119
but I loved you.

932
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:39,639
- I see you as my real granddaughter.
- I know.

933
00:40:39,719 --> 00:40:41,039
Grandma, I know everything.

934
00:40:42,159 --> 00:40:43,480
Such a good girl.

935
00:40:44,719 --> 00:40:46,199
Don't cry, Wenwen.

936
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:48,960
I'm dizzy. Really dizzy.

937
00:40:49,599 --> 00:40:50,920
Let me lie down for a bit...

938
00:40:51,400 --> 00:40:52,159
Grandma.

939
00:40:52,440 --> 00:40:53,400
I'm scared.

940
00:40:53,599 --> 00:40:54,360
Talk to me.

941
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,440
Then I won't be afraid.

942
00:40:55,760 --> 00:40:57,599
I'm here. Don't be scared.

943
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,079
You are just like Tong.

944
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,760
You both love my stories.

945
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:14,000
Tong has had it hard.

946
00:41:15,639 --> 00:41:17,800
Life has been cruel to her.

947
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:43,079
Wenwen!

948
00:41:43,119 --> 00:41:43,639
Wenwen!

949
00:41:46,119 --> 00:41:46,760
Wenwen!

950
00:41:46,840 --> 00:41:47,679
Wenwen!

951
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,360
Wenwen!

952
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:51,000
Wenwen!

953
00:41:51,039 --> 00:41:51,719
Wenwen!

954
00:41:55,199 --> 00:41:56,320
Tiezhu. Start it!

955
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,000
Try again.

956
00:42:02,199 --> 00:42:02,880
Keep going.

957
00:42:02,880 --> 00:42:04,400
The key is about to snap.

958
00:42:05,239 --> 00:42:06,800
Where did you buy this junk?

959
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:08,639
Unbelievable.

960
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:12,039
Tiezhu, it's Mr. Yu.

961
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:13,119
Answer it.

962
00:42:13,559 --> 00:42:14,559
Hello, Mr. Yu?

963
00:42:14,719 --> 00:42:16,360
I'm where you told me to go,

964
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,119
but no one is here.

965
00:42:17,119 --> 00:42:18,119
Do you have a more exact location?

966
00:42:18,119 --> 00:42:19,079
Where are they?

967
00:42:20,288 --> 00:42:23,555
(Outpatient)

968
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:28,400
Grandma, I can't get home.

969
00:42:29,039 --> 00:42:30,400
Grandma, where are you?

970
00:42:31,280 --> 00:42:33,119
Grandma, I can't find my way home.

971
00:42:33,480 --> 00:42:34,320
Grandma.

972
00:42:54,880 --> 00:42:55,519
What happened?

973
00:42:56,239 --> 00:42:56,719
What's wrong?

974
00:42:56,840 --> 00:42:57,679
I will get a doctor.

975
00:42:57,840 --> 00:42:58,400
Stay calm.

976
00:42:58,599 --> 00:42:59,280
Doctor!

977
00:42:59,519 --> 00:43:00,159
Doctor!

978
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:07,880
(Next Episode)

979
00:43:08,199 --> 00:43:09,400
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
Hi, I'm Guo Jingfei.

980
00:43:09,480 --> 00:43:11,880
(Actor, Guo Jingfei)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

981
00:43:12,199 --> 00:43:12,880
My mom and Wenwen

982
00:43:12,960 --> 00:43:13,599
have been kidnapped.

983
00:43:13,679 --> 00:43:14,760
Please, help us find them.

984
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:15,760
The four of us

985
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:16,639
have been searching all afternoon.

986
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:17,639
About the 60 million,

987
00:43:17,760 --> 00:43:19,199
we still haven't told the police.

988
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:21,000
You decide for yourselves
whether we tell them.

989
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,239
Where the vehicle disappeared...

990
00:43:22,280 --> 00:43:22,760
Where did it go?

991
00:43:22,920 --> 00:43:24,039
For a thorough sweep.

992
00:43:24,400 --> 00:43:24,800
Yes.

993
00:43:24,920 --> 00:43:25,960
How did you get targeted?

994
00:43:26,119 --> 00:43:27,199
When did they start targeting you?

995
00:43:27,679 --> 00:43:28,119
Hello?

996
00:43:28,400 --> 00:43:29,360
In half an hour,

997
00:43:29,559 --> 00:43:30,920
get to Chenchunmen Interchange.

998
00:43:31,079 --> 00:43:31,920
The kidnapper called.

999
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:32,760
Trace it now.

1000
00:43:33,119 --> 00:43:34,679
The kidnapper sent me Wenwen's location.

1001
00:43:34,840 --> 00:43:35,400
I'm forwarding it to you.

1002
00:43:35,679 --> 00:43:36,280
I'm heading there first.

1003
00:43:55,610 --> 00:44:02,620
♪The road ahead is still so long
Where have you gone?♪

1004
00:44:04,180 --> 00:44:11,340
♪Under the blazing sun
I keep heading north♪

1005
00:44:12,760 --> 00:44:20,220
♪To those who pass me by
You don't have to look at me♪

1006
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:28,640
♪Just keep walking your own way
I'll manage on my own♪

1007
00:44:31,630 --> 00:44:35,230
♪Is the rain falling hard?♪

1008
00:44:35,870 --> 00:44:39,000
♪Is there someone
to hold an umbrella for you?♪

1009
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:44,940
♪The wind has blown
the numbers off the signs♪

1010
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:47,930
♪Where am I supposed to go?♪

1011
00:44:48,730 --> 00:44:52,250
♪Can I change my mind?♪

1012
00:44:53,010 --> 00:44:56,240
♪How do I go on without you?♪

1013
00:44:57,550 --> 00:45:02,080
♪When will this
endless rain finally stop?♪

1014
00:45:02,080 --> 00:45:04,780
♪Then I'll wait for you♪

1015
00:45:04,780 --> 00:45:08,780
♪Please don't leave me waiting♪

1016
00:45:23,060 --> 00:45:26,590
♪Is the rain falling hard?♪

1017
00:45:27,410 --> 00:45:30,750
♪Is there someone
to hold an umbrella for you?♪

1018
